data.title: Seattle Dog - yum!
data.text: I stopped in here to pick up a quick bite to go, on the way to the outdoor concert at nearby Marina Park. I had heard about the Seattle Dog before, but had never tried one until now. With a good sized beef Polish sausage as the base, the creation features cream cheese, grilled onions, sliced jalapenos and sriracha sauce. Man, that was good! I can't wait for our next Kirkland concert so I can try other things on their menu. Or maybe get an other Seattle Dog? Decisions, decisions...
